    @available(iOS 10.0, *)
    open class func fetchRequest() -&gt; NSFetchRequest&lt;NSFetchRequestResult&gt;

When I was creating the fetchRequest like your case the app crash was occurring too:

    let fetchRequest = NSFetchRequest&lt;OrderType&gt;()  

